* [[波音佳丽|波音佳丽]]发行了另一款早期日本RPG《间谍大作战》。游戏改编自剧集《[[虎膽妙算|虎膽妙算]]》，将传统的[[奇幻作品|奇幻]]设定改为先带[[隐蔽类游戏|间谍]]设定<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.hardcoregaming101.net/2013/04/dark-age-of-jrpgs-2-some-games-we.html |title=Hardcore Gaming 101 - Blog: Dark Age of JRPGs (2): Some games we cannot play<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2014-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107001936/http://blog.hardcoregaming101.net/2013/04/dark-age-of-jrpgs-2-some-games-we.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fm-7.com/museum/softhouse/ponyca/540200300.html |title=Oh!FM-7：スパイ大作戦（ポニカ）<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116033132/http://fm-7.com/museum/softhouse/ponyca/540200300.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
